short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: See stats of the org in the GSOC page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
if you want to see how many time this particular org was selected or how many people it selects, this tool is best for you.

1. Visit GSoC org page for example https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2024/organizations/postman

2. Click on our extension logo and see stats for that org.
3. Don't forget to pin our extension.
